{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'm here to share my photography."},{"time":4000,"text":"Or is it photography?"},{"time":7000,"text":"Because, of course, this is a photograph"},{"time":9000,"text":"that you can't take with your camera."}]},{"cues":[{"time":11000,"text":"Yet, my interest in photography started"},{"time":13000,"text":"as I got my first digital camera"},{"time":15000,"text":"at the age of 15."},{"time":18000,"text":"It mixed with my earlier passion for drawing,"},{"time":20000,"text":"but it was a bit different,"},{"time":22000,"text":"because using the camera,"},{"time":24000,"text":"the process was in the planning instead."},{"time":27000,"text":"And when you take a photograph with a camera,"},{"time":30000,"text":"the process ends when you press the trigger."},{"time":34000,"text":"So to me it felt like photography was more about"},{"time":36000,"text":"being at the right place and the right time."},{"time":39000,"text":"I felt like anyone could do that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42000,"text":"So I wanted to create something different,"},{"time":45000,"text":"something where the process starts"},{"time":47000,"text":"when you press the trigger."},{"time":50000,"text":"Photos like this:"},{"time":52000,"text":"construction going on along a busy road."},{"time":54000,"text":"But it has an unexpected twist."},{"time":57000,"text":"And despite that,"},{"time":59000,"text":"it retains a level of realism."},{"time":62000,"text":"Or photos like these --"},{"time":65000,"text":"both dark and colorful,"},{"time":68000,"text":"but all with a common goal"},{"time":70000,"text":"of retaining the level of realism."},{"time":72000,"text":"When I say realism,"},{"time":74000,"text":"I mean photo-realism."},{"time":76000,"text":"Because, of course,"},{"time":78000,"text":"it's not something you can capture really,"},{"time":81000,"text":"but I always want it to look like it could have been captured somehow"},{"time":84000,"text":"as a photograph."},{"time":86000,"text":"Photos where you will need a brief moment to think"},{"time":89000,"text":"to figure out the trick."},{"time":91000,"text":"So it's more about capturing an idea"},{"time":93000,"text":"than about capturing a moment really."}]},{"cues":[{"time":96000,"text":"But what's the trick"},{"time":98000,"text":"that makes it look realistic?"},{"time":100000,"text":"Is it something about the details"},{"time":102000,"text":"or the colors?"},{"time":104000,"text":"Is it something about the light?"},{"time":107000,"text":"What creates the illusion?"},{"time":111000,"text":"Sometimes the perspective is the illusion."},{"time":114000,"text":"But in the end, it comes down to how we interpret the world"},{"time":117000,"text":"and how it can be realized on a two-dimensional surface."},{"time":120000,"text":"It's not really what is realistic,"},{"time":122000,"text":"it's what we think looks realistic really."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126000,"text":"So I think the basics"},{"time":128000,"text":"are quite simple."},{"time":130000,"text":"I just see it as a puzzle of reality"},{"time":133000,"text":"where you can take different pieces of reality and put it together"},{"time":136000,"text":"to create alternate reality."},{"time":139000,"text":"And let me show you a simple example."},{"time":142000,"text":"Here we have three perfectly imaginable physical objects,"},{"time":146000,"text":"something we all can relate to living in a three-dimensional world."},{"time":149000,"text":"But combined in a certain way,"},{"time":152000,"text":"they can create something that still looks three-dimensional,"},{"time":156000,"text":"like it could exist."},{"time":158000,"text":"But at the same time, we know it can't."},{"time":161000,"text":"So we trick our brains,"},{"time":163000,"text":"because our brain simply doesn't accept the fact"},{"time":165000,"text":"that it doesn't really make sense."},{"time":167000,"text":"And I see the same process"},{"time":170000,"text":"with combining photographs."},{"time":173000,"text":"It's just really about combining different realities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177000,"text":"So the things that make a photograph look realistic,"},{"time":181000,"text":"I think it's the things that we don't even think about,"},{"time":184000,"text":"the things all around us in our daily lives."},{"time":188000,"text":"But when combining photographs,"},{"time":190000,"text":"this is really important to consider,"},{"time":192000,"text":"because otherwise it just looks wrong somehow."},{"time":196000,"text":"So I would like to say that there are three simple rules to follow"},{"time":199000,"text":"to achieve a realistic result."},{"time":202000,"text":"As you can see, these images aren't really special."},{"time":205000,"text":"But combined, they can create something like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":212000,"text":"So the first rule is that photos combined"},{"time":214000,"text":"should have the same perspective."},{"time":216000,"text":"Secondly, photos combined"},{"time":218000,"text":"should have the same type of light."},{"time":221000,"text":"And these two images both fulfill these two requirements --"},{"time":224000,"text":"shot at the same height and in the same type of light."},{"time":228000,"text":"The third one is about making it impossible to distinguish"},{"time":231000,"text":"where the different images begin and end"},{"time":234000,"text":"by making it seamless."},{"time":237000,"text":"Make it impossible to say"},{"time":239000,"text":"how the image actually was composed."},{"time":241000,"text":"So by matching color, contrast and brightness"},{"time":245000,"text":"in the borders between the different images,"},{"time":247000,"text":"adding photographic defects"},{"time":249000,"text":"like depth of field,"},{"time":251000,"text":"desaturated colors and noise,"},{"time":254000,"text":"we erase the borders between the different images"},{"time":256000,"text":"and make it look like one single image,"},{"time":259000,"text":"despite the fact that one image"},{"time":261000,"text":"can contain hundreds of layers basically."}]},{"cues":[{"time":265000,"text":"So here's another example."},{"time":268000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":270000,"text":"One might think that this is just an image of a landscape"},{"time":273000,"text":"and the lower part is what's manipulated."},{"time":276000,"text":"But this image is actually entirely composed"},{"time":279000,"text":"of photographs from different locations."},{"time":282000,"text":"I personally think that it's easier to actually create a place"},{"time":285000,"text":"than to find a place,"},{"time":287000,"text":"because then you don't need to compromise"},{"time":289000,"text":"with the ideas in your head."},{"time":291000,"text":"But it does require a lot of planning."},{"time":294000,"text":"And getting this idea during winter,"},{"time":296000,"text":"I knew that I had several months to plan it,"},{"time":298000,"text":"to find the different locations"},{"time":300000,"text":"for the pieces of the puzzle basically."},{"time":303000,"text":"So for example,"},{"time":305000,"text":"the fish was captured on a fishing trip."},{"time":308000,"text":"The shores are from a different location."},{"time":310000,"text":"The underwater part was captured in a stone pit."},{"time":313000,"text":"And yeah, I even turned the house on top of the island red"},{"time":316000,"text":"to make it look more Swedish."}]},{"cues":[{"time":319000,"text":"So to achieve a realistic result,"},{"time":321000,"text":"I think it comes down to planning."},{"time":324000,"text":"It always starts with a sketch, an idea."},{"time":328000,"text":"Then it's about combining the different photographs."},{"time":331000,"text":"And here every piece is very well planned."},{"time":334000,"text":"And if you do a good job capturing the photos,"},{"time":337000,"text":"the result can be quite beautiful"},{"time":339000,"text":"and also quite realistic."},{"time":343000,"text":"So all the tools are out there,"},{"time":347000,"text":"and the only thing that limits us"},{"time":350000,"text":"is our imagination."}]},{"cues":[{"time":354000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":356000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}